    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i spent fifteen years on this theory. fifteen years of my life. and today the peer review came back... it was all wrong. every single data point was a mistake. i feel like a ghost. i look in the mirror and there's nothing there. there's no point in even being in this room anymore.",
